{%- endif %}
-- ============================================================================
-- This step captures identity information for planning purposes.
-- No SQL is executed in this step.
-- ============================================================================

/*
DATA PRODUCT IDENTITY DEFINED
=============================

Core Identity:
- Name: {{ data_product_name }}
- Domain: {{ data_product_domain }}
- Environment: {{ data_product_environment }}
- Description: {{ data_product_description }}

SCIM Configuration:
{%- if scim_prefix | upper != 'NONE' %}
- SCIM Enabled: Yes
- SCIM Prefix: {{ scim_prefix | upper }}
- Role Owner: {{ scim_prefix | upper }}_PROVISIONER
- User Assignment: Via identity provider groups
{%- else %}
- SCIM Enabled: No
- Role Owner: USERADMIN
- User Assignment: Manual GRANT statements
{%- endif %}

Naming Components (based on {{ account_strategy }}):
{%- if account_strategy == 'Single Account' %}
- Full pattern: <domain>_<dataproduct>_<zone>_<env>
- Example: {{ data_product_domain | upper }}_{{ data_product_name | upper }}_RAW_{{ data_product_environment | upper }}
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Environment-based)' %}
- Pattern: <domain>_<dataproduct>_<zone> (environment implicit)
- Example: {{ data_product_domain | upper }}_{{ data_product_name | upper }}_RAW
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain-based)' %}
- Pattern: <dataproduct>_<zone>_<env> (domain implicit)
- Example: {{ data_product_name | upper }}_RAW_{{ data_product_environment | upper }}
{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain + Environment)' %}
- Pattern: <dataproduct>_<zone> (domain and environment implicit)
- Example: {{ data_product_name | upper }}_RAW
{%- endif %}

Core Roles to be Created:
- {{ data_product_name | upper }}_ADMIN  (owns infrastructure)
- {{ data_product_name | upper }}_CREATE (creates objects)
- {{ data_product_name | upper }}_WRITE  (modifies data)
- {{ data_product_name | upper }}_RBAC   (owns access roles)
- {{ data_product_name | upper }}_READ   (read-only access)

Cost Allocation Tags:
- DOMAIN = '{{ data_product_domain | upper }}'
- ENVIRONMENT = '{{ data_product_environment | upper }}'
- DATAPRODUCT = '{{ data_product_name | upper }}'
*/

-- ============================================================================
-- VERIFICATION: Check SCIM Configuration (optional)
-- ============================================================================
-- Run these queries to verify your SCIM setup before proceeding

{%- if scim_prefix | upper != 'NONE' %}

-- Verify SCIM provisioner role exists
SHOW ROLES LIKE '{{ scim_prefix | upper }}_PROVISIONER';

-- Check SCIM security integration
SHOW SECURITY INTEGRATIONS LIKE '%{{ scim_prefix | upper }}%';

{%- else %}

-- No SCIM - verify USERADMIN is available
USE ROLE USERADMIN;
SELECT 'USERADMIN access verified' AS status;

{%- endif %}
